## Quality bar — self-check before delivering

- [ ] The "one outcome" is a single, specific decision or alignment — not "discuss."
- [ ] Every attendee is named with their role and decision power (resolved via people search).
- [ ] The run of show is time-boxed and sums to the meeting length.
- [ ] Each decision to land names exactly what {{ persona.first_name }} needs to make it.
- [ ] Any KPI on the table is shown with current value and target, sourced inline.
- [ ] Compliance/control angle is stated, even if "none identified."
- [ ] No Confidential or labeled content is pasted into the pack — summarized and linked instead.
- [ ] Talking points sound like {{ persona.first_name }}, not a generic facilitator.

If any check fails, fix it before delivering.
